description: Everyone knows you can't have a Christmas without a Christmas tree. So Sonic is helping his boyfriend Bartleby sell all of the trees on the Montclair Christmas Tree Farm. Will they be able give everyone a tree in time for Christmas? Or will they need a holiday miracle?
